{"note_id": "69a7fb36000000002802235f", "type": "normal", "title": "408考研经验贴（毫无保留版）", "desc": "408考研经验贴（毫无保留版）\n\t\n个人情况：总分360，双非科班\n备考周期：8个月\n每日学习时长：8小时左右\n分数不高，因为本科学的仅供为了通过期末考试，没有啥太大难度，和考研408确实不一样，以下仅为我个人经验及备考方法，有需要的可以看看\n#经验分享#考研 #408 #计算机考研 #计算机考研408#408考研#27考研#26考研#记录吧就现在", "video_url": "", "time": 1772616502000, "last_update_time": 1772616503000, "user_id": "66ee19bf000000000b03135d", "nickname": "不发胖只发财💰", "avatar": "https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31t9ml4fmm81g5pne36viu4qtiue4318", "liked_count": "275", "collected_count": "319", "comment_count": "45", "share_count": "30", "ip_location": "浙江", "image_list": "http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202603132137/d1035d7d0a013925a741b749c2e58f55/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031t9ngdaa626g5pne36viu4qta73g0ao!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202603132137/686355f6d5dc87e0e17002b18bbc6c22/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031t9ngdaa625g5pne36viu4qtqehnnvg!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202603132137/e4f6c50802e128f205fe1f619f79d79a/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031t9ngdaa622g5pne36viu4qtvdbm9so!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202603132137/473ded22080c8b8f8e9e993682b8497d/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031t9ngdaa621g5pne36viu4qtuim9vno!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202603132137/22db696c607391aea7e5845670216612/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031t9ngdaa62305pne36viu4qtvblq6ug!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202603132137/04fb16bf4ed161c92093d319753bf62d/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031t9ngdaa623g5pne36viu4qtii7sae8!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202603132137/79564653267abce54dfcf4b5f1957286/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031t9ngdaa62405pne36viu4qtqli8p0g!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202603132137/d92bbaf7ace504c577cb343b63201e0f/notes_pre_post/1040g3k031t9ngdaa62505pne36viu4qt2s2kkm8!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3", "tag_list": "", "last_modify_ts": 1773409085520, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/69a7fb36000000002802235f?xsec